headline.print_headline: Wasteful Leverkusen's Perfect Start Ends With Draw
headline.main: Wasteful Leverkusen's Perfect Start Ends With Draw

lead_paragraph: Bundesliga leaders Bayer Leverkusen drew 3-3 against Werder Bremen in a rollercoaster game on Friday to see their perfect start to the season end following two victories.
